	   <tr><td colspan=2>i remember how it was hard to find a croc to kill alone...&nbsp;&nbsp;lucky for me i only play really late at night..  i could pick what i wanted and kill it..  but the times i did have trouble getting kills  i would get in orc groups...  non stop action and farily decent exp...  oasis to me is still the best place to get exp til 20 imho... at 20 though i would head to south karana...  two great mobs there to kill...  one is the hermit.. can solo and i got exp til 26...  or the treants in group...  both have great exp but treants have the better loot  although you will have to group for these guys...  a lot of people like the aviak tree house  (KFC)  but i did best at these two places...  good luck<br>&nbsp;<br>Sphoenix Darkfever</td></tr>
