	   <tr><td colspan=2>When I was lev 15 and trying hard to get to 16 I was in Oasis.&nbsp;&nbsp;This is the thing...stay away from orcs - most people grouping go after them.  Go to some far off coast near the docks and hunt crocs, caimens, and maybe the occasional deep water caimen.  I advise that you have full mana to take one of those down and be ready to chain a pet when you loose the 1st one ( in case that you do loose one).  Once you hit lev 16, go get your spells and make your way to the Overthere...go to the east gate of the evil outpost, and continue down the coast heading east...the mobs that you will encounter there will be at a level that you will be able to take down with some effort =)<br>&nbsp;<br>Drackar Deathspear<br>-Officer of Balthazar's Brigade <br>Rodcet Nife</td></tr>
